snippet.title: Casual Space Themed Platformer Gameplay Trailer - Kiro the Kosmonaut
snippet.description:
Help Kiro, the brave kosmonaut to reach Pluto's orbit in one piece! On your way you will encounter numerous enemies and obstacles, utilize pick ups which will assist you in your journey and enjoy vibrant low-poly graphics and simple, yet beautiful scenery. 

Get the game free here: https://velikostudio.itch.io/kiro-the-kosmonaut

Consider supporting us:
https://www.patreon.com/VelikoStudio
